# subscript(_:)

**Instance Subscript**

Accesses an element at an index.

## Declaration

```swift
subscript(position: Int) -> DiscontiguousColumnSlice<WrappedElement>.Element { get set }
```

## Parameters

- **position**: A valid index to an element in the column slice.

## Accessing Elements

- **subscript(_:)**: Accesses a contiguous range of elements.
- **subscript(_:)**: Accesses a contiguous range of elements with a range expression.
- **subscript(_:)**: Accesses a contiguous range of elements with an unbounded range.
